fullName: /SchedulingOptimizationRegression/Provider Cancellation & Non-Billable Events Optimisation#test Open Status Drafts employee cancelation
description:
## Get Draft Schedule by ID

This endpoint retrieves a draft schedule by its unique identifier.

### Request

- Method: GET
    
- URL: `https://{{url}}/scheduling/draft-schedules/{{cancelOptimizationJobId}}`
    
- Path Parameters:
    
    - `cancelOptimizationJobId`: The unique identifier of the draft schedule to be retrieved.
        

### Response

The response for this request is a JSON object representing the draft schedule. The schema for the response can be described as follows:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    // Include the properties of the response JSON schema here
  }
}

 ```
